    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司寻求 Brookfield 和 GIP 的融资机会：《时代》杂志</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-15/thames-water-sounds-out-brookfield-gip-for-fundraising-times</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《泰晤士报》报道，泰晤士水务公司已与北美基础设施巨头 Brookfield Infrastructure Partners、Global Infrastructure Partners 以及 Stonepeak 接洽，参与一项 33 亿英镑（43 亿美元）的紧急融资计划，以拯救英国最大的供水和污水处理供应商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-15/thames-water-sounds-out-brookfield-gip-for-fundraising-times</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Sep 2024 12:07:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大航空与飞行员工会达成协议，避免罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-15/air-canada-reaches-pact-with-pilot-union-averting-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大航空与飞行员工会在最后一刻达成协议，避免了可能导致全球每天停飞 1,000 多个航班的罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-15/air-canada-reaches-pact-with-pilot-union-averting-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Sep 2024 04:50:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
